
script(type=["text/template"] id=["template_start"])
	div(class=['col-md-12'])
		p(class=['centered']) Just boiling an egg isnt hard, this site<br/>just wants to help you boil a perfect one.
	div(class=['hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-1'])
	div(class=['col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-10'])
		div#softbtn(class=['col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4'])
			img(class=['img-responsive'] src=['gfx/soft_egg.png'])
		div#mediumbtn(class=['col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4'])
			img(class=['img-responsive'] src=['gfx/medium_egg.png'])
		div#hardbtn(class=['col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4'])
			img(class=['img-responsive'] src=['gfx/hard_egg.png'])
	div(class=['hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-1'])

